_sText:
This map is relatively balanced, (with human players) and is very strategic.  Do some planning.

My first public map, still learning the ropes.

BF2 style briefing:
In an effort to frighten the UN and acquire additional power, the WTF (World Terrorist Federation) has captured an ancient temple in the deserts near the current, and deadly battleground codenamed de_dust one and two.  If the WTF continues possession of this vital base, the de_dust battlegrounds could become theirs.  Last night,  
8 Counter-Terrorists arrived by boat expecting to be brought to de_dust, instead, they were driven to this the temple, and were told to hide an a hole for 24 hours until the other 8 met up with them.  Their surprise attack to secure the base will begin upon your arrival.
